Create a futuristic, premium, and highly sophisticated Anonymous DAO Voting & Intelligent Treasury Management platform called "VEIL DAO".

## Core Concept
Build a next-generation DAO platform that combines full anonymity in voting using Zero-Knowledge proofs with intelligent on-chain treasury management.

## Key Features

- Anonymous voting with ZK proofs (voter identity and choice hidden)
- Real-time private vote tally
- Smart treasury dashboard with multi-chain asset overview
- AI Treasury Assistant for insights and suggestions
- Proposal creation with treasury impact preview
- Beautiful governance analytics
- Dark cyberpunk elegant design with purple/cyan accents

## Tech Stack & Design
- React 19 + TypeScript + Vite
- Tailwind + shadcn/ui + glassmorphism
- Framer Motion for premium animations
- Dark futuristic UI (institutional + cyberpunk feel)

Make this feel like the most advanced anonymous DAO tool in crypto.
